---
title: "US32 — Access all Free features"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>HomeShell
  participant C as «Control»<br/>Authenticate
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile · Subscription
  A->>B: open the app (signed in)
  B->>C: loadProfile(userId)
  C->>E: fetchProfile(userId)
  E-->>C: Profile (role = premium)
  C->>E: fetchSubscription(userId)
  E-->>C: Subscription (isPremium = true)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (premium)
  B-->>A: all Free features + premium surfaces<br/>(no cap banner, no locks)
  note over E: fetchProfile / fetchSubscription<br/>via ProfileGateway → Supabase (RLS)
